               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280410-245-cd1304" type="crimeDate">3d of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-245-off1303 t18280410-245-cd1304"></join>, 3 sovereigns, the monies of 
                     <persName id="t18280410-245-victim1364" type="victimName">
                        Charles 
                        Flackney
                     <interp inst="t18280410-245-victim1364" type="surname" value="Flackney"></interp>
